      -->
  </archetypedescription>

  <archetypeprimaryabilities>
      <list> 
        <li>Str:+0, End:+0, Ag:+0, Spd:-1, Per:+2, or</li>
        <li>Str:+0, End:+0, Ag:+0, Spd:+0, Per:+1</li>
      </list>
  </archetypeprimaryabilities>
  <archetypeinitialabilities>
    <p>
      All Red Mages start with the following skills:
      ✱language.merovingian_4, ✱language.inochian_3, and one of ✱language.aquilonian_3, ✱language.occitan_3 or ✱language.lagashi_3,
      ✱physical.dodge_2 and one of ✱physical.run_3, ✱physical.sixth_sense_3, or ✱physical.sure_feet_3.
      Gain ✱social.contacts[College-of-Mages]_3, ✱social.etiquette[Laibstadt]_3 and ✱lore.book_learning_2.
      Gain two of ✱lore.alchemy_2, ✱lore.antiquarian_2, ✱lore.natural_history_2, or ✱lore.history_2.
      Gain ✱sword.strike_1, ✱sword.parry_2, ✱staff.strike_1, and ✱staff.parry_2.
      Gain ✱elemental.lore_2, and one of ✱elemental.smoke_weasel_1 or ✱elemental.burning_hands_1.
      Gain ✱arcana.lore_1, ✱arcana.true_sight_1 and either ✱arcana.ignis_1 and ✱elemental.mist_1, or ✱arcana.aegis_1 and ✱arcana.incendo_1. 
    </p>

